21#ifndef _ELF_VAX_H
22#define _ELF_VAX_H
23
24#include "elf/reloc-macros.h"
25
26/* Relocation types. */
27START_RELOC_NUMBERS (elf_vax_reloc_type)
28 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_NONE, 0) /* No reloc */
29 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_32, 1) /* Direct 32 bit */
30 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_16, 2) /* Direct 16 bit */
31 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_8, 3) /* Direct 8 bit */
32 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_PC32, 4) /* PC relative 32 bit */
33 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_PC16, 5) /* PC relative 16 bit */
34 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_PC8, 6) /* PC relative 8 bit */
35 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_GOT32, 7) /* 32 bit PC relative GOT entry */
36 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_PLT32, 13) /* 32 bit PC relative PLT address */
37 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_COPY, 19) /* Copy symbol at runtime */
38 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_GLOB_DAT, 20) /* Create GOT entry */
39 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_JMP_SLOT, 21) /* Create PLT entry */
40 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_RELATIVE, 22) /* Adjust by program base */
41 /* These are GNU extensions to enable C++ vtable garbage collection. */
42 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_GNU_VTINHERIT, 23)
43 RELOC_NUMBER (R_VAX_GNU_VTENTRY, 24)
44END_RELOC_NUMBERS (R_VAX_max)
45
46/* Processor specific flags for the ELF header e_flags field. */
47#define EF_VAX_NONPIC 0x0001 /* Object contains non-PIC code */
48#define EF_VAX_DFLOAT 0x0100 /* Object contains D-Float insn. */
49#define EF_VAX_GFLOAT 0x0200 /* Object contains G-Float insn. */
50
51#endif
